meta.title: Little Bill mixes Tomato and Milk

ttsdata.text: Hey mama.
Oh, good evening Little Bill. It's not time for dinner yet.
I know. I was just wondering what was, for dinner.
Oh, I already told you guys. Fried tomatos with sprinkled pepper and cheese.
Yummy. Though can I not have peppa. I hate peppa.
We'll see. Pepper's good for you though.
Can I milk though mama. I'm thirsty.
Okay, but no cookies until after dinner. If I see you with cookies you will be grounded. Remember what happened last time?
Oh okay, no cookies. Yeah, I remember. I had a stomach ache and threw up.
Oh, crap. I forgot about the laundry downstairs. I'll be back.
I hope the clothes aren't wrinkled.
I'm real hungry now. But I can't have cookies.
Wait!! But what about that tomato.
I could snack on this before dinner. Then I'd be healthhy. Mama wants me to be healthy. Right?
Hey, I wonder what this tastes like with milk.
Wow. Looks weird.
Oh my god. This taste awesome. I should show my friends this.
Little Bill? Is that you climbed on the counter?
No! No mama. I'm in the living room watching Kinng Of Queens.
I gotta get outta here.
Bill? You in here?
What the hell happened to my tomato?
Yo Andrew. Guess what?
What is it Bill?
I invented a new juice. I call it, Tilk.
Tilk? What kind of name is that?
Just try it and see.
Wow. This is. This is.
Yo let me try it.
Bill, this is. Nasty. Ugh. Oh my. God.
That's one of the worst things i've tasted in my whole 6 years of life.
Brah, that shit is nasty a f.
Bill what is wrong with you? Oh my god. I can't get the taste out.
What's all that? Is that throw up? Oh god. The smell.
Oh god. I'm tripping.
Fuck me. I'm swimming in my own and other peoples throw up.
